Usage: update_analysis_view [-help] -name <existingAnalysisViewName> { [-constraint_mode <newModeName>] [-delay_corner <newDelayCornerObj>][-latency_file <string>] }

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-constraint_mode <newModeName>       # Specifies the name of the constraint
                                     # mode to associate with this analysis
                                     # view (string, optional)
-delay_corner <newDelayCornerObj>    # Specifies the name of the delay
                                     # calculation corner object to associate
                                     # with this analysis view (string, optional)
-latency_file <string>               # Specifies the latency filename
                                     # (string, optional)
-name <existingAnalysisViewName>     # Specifies the name of the analysis view
                                     # being updated (string, required)